Package: wiritttes
Type: Package
Title: WIRITTE simulation
Version: 1.0
Author: Richel Bilderbeek <richel@richelbilderbeek.nl>
Maintainer: Richel Bilderbeek <richel@richelbilderbeek.nl>
Description: What if reproduction isolation takes time to establish?
    This package first simulates a PBD phylogeny, in which reproductive
    isolation does take time to establish. From those phylogenies, DNA
    sequences are simulation and analysed using BEAST2. BEAST2 does not
    assume that reproductive isolation takes time to establish. The
    analysis of the resulting data is done by the wiritttea package.
